      "Text": "Security update for openvswitch",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for openvswitch fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-5265: heap over-read in ICMP error response generation (bsc#1262498).\n- CVE-2026-5367: heap over-read in OVN DHCPv6 client ID processing (bsc#1262499).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
